metadata.name: The backs of tigers
metadata.description: Somali Landscape: A mesmerizing image captured by satellite showcases the unique landscape of Somalia that resembles tiger skins or tiger backs. The intricate patterns and textures of the land resemble the stripes on the majestic coat of a tiger, creating a captivating visual spectacle. The rugged terrain, with its undulating hills, valleys, and plateaus, forms a stunning natural pattern that resembles the distinct markings of a tiger. This satellite image of the Somali landscape serves as a testament to the awe-inspiring beauty and diversity found in our world's landscapes, showcasing nature's artistic mastery on display.
